name: watcher | dots and thoughts
description: the fourth part of the nine piece series 'dots and thoughts'. < there is a little man. sitting behind the pupil. watching what happens in the world. whenever you think about the past. that little man goes into a dark room behind the head.  shifts the files of past. whenever you think about the future. that little man goes into a dark room again and reports future predictions. remember this. let that little man rest and just watch. > IG: elfbyl
